  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 37-13-8, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO ENACT THE \"PERIOD OF QUIET REFLECTION ACT\"; TO PROVIDE THAT IN EACH PUBLIC SCHOOL CLASSROOM, THE LOCAL SCHOOL GOVERNING BOARD SHALL REQUIRE A BRIEF PERIOD OF QUIET REFLECTION FOR NOT MORE THAN 60 SECONDS AT THE OPENING OF EVERY SCHOOL DAY; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
